  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756031576-FFUZE5L38VU6GJLE5I2R/19a-IMG_3397.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>So I have a ton to share today - including the new addition to the studio right by the door - the world map cut out of vinyl using my <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/die-cutting/silhouette-cameo-bundle?aff=6cc2c70f\">Silhouette</a>. I was a bit nervous while applying the vinyl to the wall, but think it turned out quite lovely. And it was so easy. I used <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/digital/digital-stamp-brushes/penny-arcade-scrapbook-kit-stamps?aff=6cc2c70f\">this Penny Arcade digital file</a> and converted the .png file in my Silhouette software using <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/37711971\">this awesome instructional video from Heidi Swapp</a>. Also, please ignore those little wispy baby hairs that are coming in. Yikes.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19b-IMG_3392.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756067635-KG4MWREO5QNX6PQL4W82/19b-IMG_3392.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"19c-IMG_3395.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756067636-Y3JZLWX7HHP3R3IRJBNF/19c-IMG_3395.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19d-PENNY-ARCADE-Reveal_header.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756068554-YMRQHQW8FMR6NLALZW4Q/19d-PENNY-ARCADE-Reveal_header.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Seriously, these <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/penny-arcade?aff=6cc2c70f\">Penny Arcade kits</a> were so fun to work with. My layouts came together with ease, and with a limited time frame, I really appreciated that. This month, I challenged myself to use multiple photos for every single layout. Mostly because I realize that I have a lot of photos hanging around and want to put them to good use. Here's what I made using the scrapbook kits, including some photos of how the pages came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19e-cheers.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756120004-4N0I84SMT4BQF0MBRO8T/19e-cheers.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19f-KP.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756119149-523E9IJ2FEOQ78VNQC5A/19f-KP.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19g-20140624-222616-80776381.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756119867-03B998S112EGMWY1D7B5/19g-20140624-222616-80776381.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19h-20140624-222617-80777144.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756120340-UITXFASZW9VF7OC1RIQC/19h-20140624-222617-80777144.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19i-20140624-222618-80778641.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756121120-NFJBPPBW0WN5USSMW8F6/19i-20140624-222618-80778641.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19j-20140624-222645-80805901.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756120809-A3631GASN1S09O8LVPUZ/19j-20140624-222645-80805901.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19k-20140624-222644-80804888.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756121882-7NXUIIL0DIFK2CAK3IXP/19k-20140624-222644-80804888.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19l-goodstuff.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756125153-X7V8XCHYPSP3GBU2WX54/19l-goodstuff.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I designed the stamp set in the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/spun-sugar?aff=6cc2c70f\">Spun Sugar add-on</a>, so other than the world map silhouette, it may be difficult to distinguish what's my writing in the layout and what is actually stamped.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19m-20140624-222648-80808998.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756182520-PDZ0ZKC1702NIRAGLMZ8/19m-20140624-222648-80808998.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19n-20140624-222650-80810007.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756182518-YWL9LQ2BAE0CV3B2Y9O2/19n-20140624-222650-80810007.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19o-20140624-222646-80806818.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756183047-KDVJRRSOVR9GXN9VXRM4/19o-20140624-222646-80806818.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19p-truestory.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756184507-LM5M1O8E5B79RFLR46L3/19p-truestory.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>It was easy to play catch up on some of Jack's album using the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/penny-arcade-project-life-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Project Life kits</a>. Once again, these aren't full week spreads, as I am just approaching this album in a different way, just documenting how I feel at the moment. We went from Ventura to Vegas, and I covered lots of fun little bits.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19q-PL.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756223666-LSP2LGI5ZG4FM1IO75X4/19q-PL.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19r-PL2.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598756223713-NL2A8YH8EU3S9NZXH94O/19r-PL2.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>You can shop for all the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/penny-arcade?aff=6cc2c70f\">Penny Arcade kits here</a> and see <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/project-folders/4318-penny-arcade?aff=6cc2c70f\">all my projects here</a>.</p><p>Keep in mind that <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\">subscribers</a> can shop the pre-sale each month at noon EST on the 27th. Others need to wait until the clock strikes midnight tonight. <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\">Become a subscriber</a> and get in on all the benefits and rewards that <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a> has to offer!</p>"
